#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:1 of
msgid "Encode target labels with value between 0 and n_classes-1."
msgstr "使用介于 0 和 n_classes-1 之间的值对目标标签进行编码。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:3 of
msgid ""
"This transformer should be used to encode target values, *i.e.* `y`, and "
"not the input `X`."
msgstr "此转换器应用于编码目标值，即 `y`，而不是输入 `X`。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:6 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <preprocessing_targets>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <preprocessing_targets>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:10 of
msgid "Holds the label for each class."
msgstr "保存每个类别的标签。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder of
msgid "type"
msgstr "类型"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:12 of
msgid "ndarray of shape (n_classes,)"
msgstr "形状为 (n_classes,) 的 ndarray"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:16 of
msgid ":py:obj:`OrdinalEncoder`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:17 of
msgid "Encode categorical features using an ordinal encoding scheme."
msgstr "使用序数编码方案对分类特征进行编码。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`OneHotEncoder`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:20 of
msgid "Encode categorical features as a one-hot numeric array."
msgstr "将分类特征编码为独热（one-hot）数值数组。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:23 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:24 of
msgid "`LabelEncoder` can be used to normalize labels."
msgstr "`LabelEncoder` 可用于标准化标签。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_encoder.LabelEncoder:37 of
msgid ""
"It can also be used to transform non-numerical labels (as long as they "
"are hashable and comparable) to numerical labels."
msgstr "它还可以用于将非数值标签（只要它们是可哈希和可比较的）转换为数值标签。"

